<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="3" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然然<colour id="65535" />店里卖的灌木，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以很好地利用立体空间来种植，<delay20 />
能让人获得<delay8 />更精致的园艺体验。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正好，<delay8 />现在是地球日的活动期间，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可以尽情地买上许多<delay8 />
灌木树苗哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你知道吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />灌木在种植的时候<delay8 />可以不留空隙哦！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />围着家周围种上一圈，<delay8 />就是矮树篱笆啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用植物来装扮<delay8 />自己的家<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不觉得这很棒吗？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />花儿<delay8 />可以戴在身上作饰品，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以说，<delay8 />自己种植一些喜欢的种类，
也是不错的选择呢！
<colour id="3" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然然<colour id="65535" />那儿售卖的，<delay8 />
稀有种类的花朵种子<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />选哪个好呢？<delay8 />真让人纠结！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">就算<delay8 />平时非常注意，<delay20 />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但在赶时间时还是会不小心踩到花儿<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样的情况<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />你遇到过吗？
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实<delay8 />只要用栅栏围在花周围，<delay20 />
就能形成一个非常漂亮的花坛，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且还能防止踩踏到花儿们呢！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />我可从来没有<delay20 />
把花儿踩坏过哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />植物<delay20 />不仅可以净化空气，<delay20 />
还能使观者的心灵<delay8 />得到净化<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得它们拥有<delay8 />这样神奇的力量！
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然它们的存在看来平凡，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我们应该<delay8 />一直对它们抱以感激之心，<delay8 />
而不仅限于今天一天！<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>